parameters.jsCode:
const data = $input.first().json.body;

const normalizeValue = (val) => {
  if (Array.isArray(val)) {
    return val[0] || '';
  } else if (val && typeof val === 'object') {
    return val.value || ''; // Adjust this if your object has a different structure
  } else {
    return val || '';
  }
};

const result = {
  id: '=ROW()-1',
  uuid: data.uuid || '',
  type: data.type || '',
  project: data.project || '',
  date_requested: data.date_requested || '',
  service_request_no: data.service_request_no || '',
  department: data.department || '',
  module: data.module || '',
  system_form_no: data.system_form_no || '',
  system_form_name: data.system_form_name || '',
  concern_type_new: data.concern_type_new ?? 'No',
  concern_type_rev: data.concern_type_rev ?? 'No',
  concern_type_del: data.concern_type_del ?? 'No',
  concern_type_cos: data.concern_type_cos ?? 'No',
  priority_set: data.priority_set ?? 'No',
  committed_date: data.committed_date || '',
  priority_immediate: data.priority_immediate ?? 'No',
  priority_add: data.priority_add ?? 'No',
  user: data.user || '',
  user_id: data.user_id || '',
  department_head: data.department_head || '',
  department_head_id: data.department_head_id || '',
  it_head: data.it_head || '',
  it_head_id: data.it_head_id || '',
  integrator: data.integrator || '',
  integrator_id: data.integrator_id || '',
  developer: data.developer || '',
  developer_id: data.developer_id || '',
  qa: data.qa || '',
  qa_id: data.qa_id || '',
  print_option_as_req: data.print_option_as_req ?? 'No',
  print_out_date: data.print_out_date || '',
  print_option_sys_print: data.print_option_sys_print ?? 'No',
  system_print_date: data.system_print_date || '',
  print_option_modified: data.print_option_modified ?? 'No',
  patch_date: data.patch_date || '',
  memo: normalizeValue(data.memo),
  req_status: normalizeValue(data.req_status),
  cylix_status: normalizeValue(data.cylix_status),
  dev_status: normalizeValue(data.dev_status),
  concern_type_data: data.concern_type_data || '',
  concern_type_bugs: data.concern_type_bugs || '',
};

return [{ json: { data: result } }];
